snippet: Newt Gingrich reported raising just $808,000 dollars during the three-month period ending Sept. 30.
lead_paragraph: Newt Gingrich, the former House speaker who endured mass departure of his top aides in June and has struggled to keep his campaign afloat, reported raising just $808,000 dollars during the three-month period ending Sept. 30, according to papers filed with the Federal Election Commission on Saturday.

headline.main: Gingrich Raises Under $1 Million; Campaign in the Red
